data.description: Stunning brand new renovation located on a fantastic block in booming Point Breeze! This fabulous 3-story, 4 bedroom/3 bathroom, 1800 sq. ft. home has it all!  Beautiful kitchen & bathrooms, high ceilings, gorgeous hardwood floors, dual zoned heating & air, and 2 amazing outdoor spaces!  One is a large private rear patio and the other a spectacular roof deck with 360 degrees of city views!  Another very special feature of this home is every room is wired for internet & cable, and the whole house is hardwired for security.  The third floor is designed to be a full master suite floor!  Finished basement with plenty of storage space.  A very impressive home.
